usb: host: xhci-rcar: Add a helper macro to set xhci_plat_priv

To avoid copy-and-paste setting of xhci_plat_priv for R-Car SoCs,
this patch add a helper macro SET_XHCI_PLAT_PRIV_FOR_RCAR.

